Package: VMAorder
Title: Tools for Vector Moving Average Order Estimation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Enxin", "Qin", email = "19719272939@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for simulating vector moving-average models,
    computing lagged cross-covariance matrices, constructing VMA order
    statistics, estimating model order, testing stationarity, and visualizing
    statistic curves.
